snippet.title: Wall-E 2600 - Atari 2600 Homebrew
snippet.description:
Hey kids, do you like Wall-E? You do? Then great news! Now you can help Wall-E clean up trash on your Atari 2600, from the homebrew developer Rabbit 2600!

Go around the junkyard and clean up all that garbage, but watch out! Electrical storms are brewing and if Wall-E is hit, he shuts down.

Wall-E (C) Disney / Pixar
Developed with batari Basic
Download: https://forums.atariage.com/topic/213777-wall-e-2600/
